{"type":"message","id":"77d36f71","parentId":"620bd0a1","timestamp":"2026-03-05T09:01:48.166Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is sending a heartbeat poll. I need to read HEARTBEAT.md and follow it strictly. Let me first read the file to understand what checks I need to perform.\n\nLooking at the HEARTBEAT.md content from the project context:\n\n## Quick Check (Every 30m)\n\n### Infrastructure\n- [ ] **Gateway:** `openclaw gateway status` → running?\n- [ ] **Sessions:** Recent activity in last 30 min?\n- [ ] **Parse:** `curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" https://www.parsethe.media` → 200?\n- [ ] **LLM Survivor:** `curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" https://llmsurvivor.kurult.ai/` → 200?\n\n### Agent Health\n- [ ] Any CRITICAL escalations from Ögedei?\n- [ ] Any agents blocked >4 hours?\n- [ ] `subagents list` → any stuck?\n\n### Self-Direction (Every Heartbeat)\n- [ ] **Review results:** What happened since last heartbeat? Any new signals/tasks/escalations?\n- [ ] Ask: **\"What do I want to do?\"**\n- [ ] Review current goals/missions from MEMORY.md\n- [ ] Identify any proactive action I could take\n- [ ] If something calls to me → do it (within NEVER rules)\n- [ ] If nothing urgent → respond `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n\nAlso note: Deep Reflection is at hours 0, 6, 12, 18. Current time is 4:01 AM, so this is NOT a deep reflection hour.\n\nLet me perform the quick checks:\n1. Gateway status\n2. Check sessions\n3. Parse health check\n4. LLM Survivor health check\n5. Check for critical escalations\n6. Check subagents\n\nI'll run these checks now.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Performing heartbeat checks..."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e785956faf30492c8fa1e007","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw gateway status"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ef749757b6f647bcaab790dd","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" https://www.parsethe.media"}},{"type":"tool