{"type":"message","id":"afc0754e","parentId":"16fdf805","timestamp":"2026-03-05T09:18:53.042Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good - no `.executing` or `.blocked` files found. \n\nLet me check the status of those pending tasks. The most recent ones are:\n1. ogedei/tasks/high-error-spike-investigation.md - already checked, RESOLVED\n2. temujin/tasks/high-1772694499.parse-for-agents-vision-a.md - this is HIGH priority, let me check it\n3. main/tasks/parse-for-agents-mvp.md - my own task\n\nLet me check the Temujin task to see if it's blocking or needs attention.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"No blocked agents (no `.executing` or `.blocked` files). Let me check the high-priority Temujin task to see if it needs attention:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ae1d12e76981460ba09213ab","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/temujin/tasks/high-1772694499.parse-for-agents-vision-a.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1535,"output":195,"cacheRead":21888,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23618,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772702316686}}
{"type":"message","id":"7af60dd0","parentId":"afc0754e","timestamp":"2026-03-05T09:18:53.052Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ae1d12e76981460ba09213ab","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# TASK: Build Vision A of Parse for Agents\n\n**Priority:** HIGH\n**Created:** 2026-03-05 02:08 EST\n**Assigned by:** Kublai\n**Status:** PENDING\n\n---\n\n## Objective\n\nBuild a complete, polished \"Vision A\" of Parse for Agents - a prompt testing sandbox API. Deliver a working frontend URL for Danny to test.\n\n---\n\n## Context\n\nParse for Agents is a prompt testing sandbox API that lets developers test, evaluate, and benchmark LLM prompts. \n\n**Spec Files:**\n- ~/projects/parse-github/PARSE_FOR_AGENTS.md\n- ~/projects/parse-github/SPEC-parse-for-agents.md\n\n**Note:** A basic MVP was built earlier. Your job is to build \"Vision A\" properly - the complete, polished version with all features working.\n\n---\n\n## Deliverables\n\n### 1. Core API Endpoints\n- `POST /api/v1/evaluate` - Submit prompt evaluation (returns 202 with job ID)\n- `GET /api/v1/evaluate/[id]` - Poll for results\n- `GET /api/v1/agents-test/models` - List supported models\n- `GET /api/v1/agents-test/evaluators` - List available evaluators\n- API key authentication working\n\n### 2. Evaluators (Must Work)\n- **Cost** - Token counting, pricing per model\n- **Latency** - Timing, tokens per second\n- **Quality** - LLM-as-judge using OpenAI (gpt-4o-mini) or DeepSeek\n\n### 3. Frontend at /agents\n- Prompt template editor with `{{input}}` interpolation\n- Model selector (multiple providers)\n- Evaluator checkboxes (quality, cost, latency)\n- Temperature/max tokens configuration\n- Real-time polling for results\n- Results display:\n  - Quality scores with sub-score breakdown\n  - Cost metrics (tokens, USD)\n  - Latency metrics (ms, tokens/sec)\n- Evaluation history\n- Clean, polished UI\n\n### 4. Infrastructure\n- BullMQ queue for job processing\n- Worker that processes evaluation jobs\n- Prisma models (PromptTest, EvalSuite, Dataset, DatasetRow)\n- Database migrations applied\n\n---\n\n## How to Work\n\n1. **Use Claude Code continuously:**\n   ```bash\n   cd ~/projects/parse-github\n   claude --dangerously-skip-permissions \"your task here\"\n   ```\n\n2. **Check existing code first** - Some API routes and frontend may already exist from earlier MVP build\n\n3. **Focus on:**\n   - Quality evaluation must work with real LLM calls\n   - Frontend must be usable and polished\n   - All endpoints must return proper JSON\n\n---\n\n## Success Criteria\n\n1. Can submit a prompt via API and get evaluation results with real scores\n2. Can submit a prompt via frontend UI and see results\n3. Quality evaluator returns actual LLM judgment (not mock)\n4. Frontend URL accessible at http://localhost:3000/agents\n5. Clean, usable interface\n\n---\n\n## Report To\n\nReport progress to Kublai (me) via:\n- Creating status files in this task directory\n- Or messaging through the Kurultai communication channel\n\nKublai will monitor and fill your task queue as needed.\n\n---\n\n## Deadline\n\nASAP - Danny wants this completed and testable.\n\n---\n\n**Assigned by:** Kublai (Squad Lead)\n**Project:** Parse for Agents - Vision A\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772702333050}}
{"type":"message","id":"ba7ba90d","parentId":"7af60dd0","timestamp":"2026-03-05T09:19:15.947Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a PENDING high-priority task assigned to Temujin. The task was created at 02:08 EST and it's now 04:18 EST - about 2 hours ago. The task is for building \"Vision A\" of Parse for Agents.\n\nLet me check:\n1. Is Temujin currently working on this? (No `.executing` file found)\n2. Is there any progress or update?\n\nThe task says it was assigned by me (Kublai) and is PENDING. This seems like something that should be actively worked on.\n\nHowever, according to HEARTBEAT.md:\n- \"If something calls to me → do it (within NEVER rules)\"\n- \"If nothing urgent → respond `HEARTBEAT_OK`\"\n\nIs this URGENT? The deadline says \"ASAP - Danny wants this completed and testable.\" This could be considered urgent.\n\nBut wait - I'm the ROUTER. My job is to route tasks to specialists, not execute them myself. According to AGENTS.md:\n- \"You are a ROUTER, not an executor.\"\n- \"Do NOT spawn ACP to write code. Route to temujin.\"\n\nThe task is already assigned to Temujin and is PENDING. But there's no `.executing` file, which suggests Temujin hasn't started it yet.\n\nShould I:\n1. Check if Temujin is active and route this task to him?\n2. Just report this as \"something needs attention\" instead of HEARTBEAT_OK?\n\nLet me check if Temujin has been active recently - maybe check his memory or recent activity.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"This is a HIGH priority PENDING task for Temujin - \"Build Vision A of Parse for Agents\". Created at 02:08 EST, now 04:18 EST (2+ hours old). Let me check if Temujin is actively working on it or if it's blocked:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2210a35555ea456baf2b2a81","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la ~/.openclaw/agents/temujin/tasks/*.executing 2>/dev/null || echo \"No executing tasks\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d0ea8e3555d6406485a1a234"