{"type":"message","id":"cb12347e","parentId":"d9c21df5","timestamp":"2026-03-05T09:21:29.863Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The session send is also restricted - I can only send to my own session tree, not to other agents' sessions.\n\nSo my options are limited:\n1. I cannot message Temujin directly via message (he's not a Signal contact)\n2. I cannot send to Temujin's session via sessions_send (visibility restriction)\n3. I could potentially modify his task files directly\n\nBut wait - looking at the architecture:\n- Each agent has their own workspace\n- They have their own tasks directories\n- Tasks are assigned via files\n\nThe task is already in his directory. What I could do is:\n1. Add a `.urgent` flag or update the task to indicate it's stalled\n2. Or create a new escalation task\n\nBut actually, thinking about this more practically:\n- The task is already in his directory\n- It's already marked as HIGH priority\n- Temujin should pick it up on his next heartbeat\n\nThe question is: should I report this as \"needing attention\" in my heartbeat response?\n\nLooking at HEARTBEAT.md:\n- \"If Something Needs Attention\"\n- \"Report: 1. What's blocked 2. Which agent is affected 3. What decision/action is needed\"\n\nI think the answer is YES - this is something that needs attention:\n1. What's blocked: HIGH priority task \"Build Vision A of Parse for Agents\" has been PENDING 2+ hours\n2. Which agent is affected: Temujin\n3. What decision/action is needed: Temujin needs to start work or report blocker; may need manual intervention to wake Temujin if he's not heartbeating\n\nLet me check one more thing - is Temujin's heartbeat even running? I should check if there are cron jobs or other mechanisms that should be triggering his heartbeats.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Session visibility restricted - can't message Temujin directly. Let me check if Temujin's heartbeat is even running:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9e5bf45d02384d8990b4dba2","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"list"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":25919,"output":410,"cacheRead":1600,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27929,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772702465718}}
{"type":"message","id":"d215b13a","parentId":"cb12347e","timestamp":"2026-03-05T09:21:29.885Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9e5bf45d02384d8990b4dba2","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"367c11f7-a5ab-4890-b0c4-c678d3292de2\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"name\": \"heartbeat-watchdog\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1772596880657,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1772702305201,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"every\",\n        \"everyMs\": 300000,\n        \"anchorMs\": 1772596939203\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Run the tick. Execute: bash ~/.openclaw/agents/main/scripts/watchdog-gather.sh. Read the output. If DECISION is healthy, log: [timestamp] WATCHDOG_LLM | status=healthy | accepted_bash=yes | note=nominal. If degraded/down, assess and log accordingly. ONE bash command, ONE log line.\",\n        \"model\": \"zai-coding/glm-5\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 600\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1772702555390,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1772702255390,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 49811,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"lastDelivered\": false\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"a1b2c3d4-tock-4e5f-6a7b-8c9d0e1f2a3b\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"name\": \"tock-gather\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1772610000000,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1772701319753,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"1,31 * * * *\",\n        \"staggerMs\": 60000\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"k