n_progress/blocked), 2) Calculate % complete, 3) Identify blockers (>48h no progress), 4) Check if on track for deadline. Generate concise summary: Goal name, % complete, days remaining, key wins, blockers, next milestones. Include revenue metrics for Parse goal (MRR, paying users, conversion rate). Report format: '📊 Daily Progress [Date] \\\\n\\\\n## Goal Name\\\\n- Progress: X% complete, Y days remaining\\\\n- ✅ Wins: [list]\\\\n- ⚠️ Blockers: [list]\\\\n- 📍 Next: [milestone]'. Keep under 500 tokens. Send via Signal.\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"signal\",\n        \"to\": \"+15165643945\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1772712000000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1772666032899,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 71462,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"lastDelivered\": true\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"76c16bd7-2ef4-4bc1-816b-7fdd91df4ecf\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"Architecture Verification - 12hr Check\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1772344228817,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1772687523796,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"expr\": \"0 */12 * * *\",\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"staggerMs\": 300000\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"ARCHITECTURE VERIFICATION TASK: Review the current codebase and compare against ARCHITECTURE.md to ensure accuracy. Check for: 1) New files/directories not documented, 2) Changes to agent structure, 3) New operational systems, 4) Outdated Change Log entries, 5) New tools/capabilities, 6) Changes to memory architecture. Read ARCHITECTURE.md, then scan the codebase (ls -la ~/.openclaw/agents/main/, check 