{"type":"message","id":"df98a51b","parentId":"15562d69","timestamp":"2026-03-05T09:32:49.091Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Same situation as before:\n1. No `.executing` tasks for Temujin\n2. Most recent completions are from Mar 3 (days ago)\n3. The HIGH priority task `high-1772694499.parse-for-agents-vision-a.md` is still there (created Mar 5 02:13)\n\nThe task is still PENDING - no progress in the 13 minutes since my last heartbeat.\n\nNow I need to think about what I can do:\n\n1. The task is still stalled\n2. I cannot message Temujin directly (tried last time, failed)\n3. The hourly Kurultai Reflection should run soon (it's 4:31, and the cron runs at the top of the hour)\n\nWait - let me check when the Hourly Kurultai Reflection last ran and when it will run next.\n\nLooking at the cron list from earlier:\n- \"Hourly Kurultai Reflection\" - cron expr: \"0 * * * *\" (at minute 0 of every hour)\n- lastRunAtMs: 1772701356484\n- nextRunAtMs: 1772704956478\n\nLet me convert those timestamps to see when it last ran and when it will run next.\n\nCurrent time: 4:31 AM EST on March 5, 2026\n- That's roughly 1772703060000 milliseconds since epoch (estimate)\n\nlastRunAtMs: 1772701356484 - this was about 1:02 AM (about 3.5 hours ago)\nnextRunAtMs: 1772704956478 - this would be around 5:02 AM (about 30 minutes from now)\n\nHmm, that doesn't match up with hourly. Let me think about this more carefully.\n\nActually, I should check the current time in milliseconds. The current time is 4:31 AM EST on March 5, 2026.\n\nMarch 5, 2026 4:31 AM EST = March 5, 2026 9:31 AM UTC\n\nLet me calculate: \n- January 1, 1970 00:00:00 UTC = 0\n- March 5, 2026 00:00:00 UTC would be...\n\nActually, I don't need to calculate this precisely. The point is that the Hourly Kurultai Reflection runs hourly, and it should run soon (at 5:00 AM or thereabouts).\n\nBut here's the issue: the task has been pending since 2:08 AM, and it's now 4:31 AM. That's 2 hours and 23 minutes. The reflection job should have run at least twice in that time (at 3:00 AM and 4:00 AM).\n\nWhy hasn't Temujin picked up this task?\n\nPossible reasons:\n1. The reflection job is for REFLECTION, not task execution\n2. There's a separate mechanism for task execution (heartbeat-task-executor.py)\n3. The heartbeat master daemon is supposed to handle this but isn't working for Temujin\n\nLet me check if the heartbeat master daemon is even aware of this task. Maybe I should look at its logs.\n\nActually, I think I'm overthinking this again. The key question is:\n\n**Should I report this as \"something needs attention\" or say HEARTBEAT_OK?**\n\nLooking at HEARTBEAT.md:\n- \"If Something Needs Attention: Report what's blocked, which agent is affected, what decision/action is needed\"\n- \"If nothing urgent → respond `HEARTBEAT_OK`\"\n\nI reported this last time. The situation hasn't changed. Should I keep reporting it?\n\nThe instructions say \"Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats.\" Does that mean I shouldn't report the same issue twice?\n\nActually, I think this refers to not inferring tasks from old chat history - i.e., don't make up tasks based on what was discussed previously. It doesn't mean I can't report an ongoing issue.\n\nThe task is STILL stalled. It's been 2+ hours. The deadline is ASAP. This is still something that needs attention.\n\nBut wait - what can actually be DONE about this? I've already tried:\n1. Messaging Temujin (failed - not a Signal contact)\n2. Sessions_send to Temujin (failed - visibility restricted)\n\nThe only way to fix this is:\n1. Wait for the hourly reflection to pick it up\n2. Manually intervene (human action)\n3. Check if the heartbeat master daemon is working\n\nLet me check the heartbeat master daemon logs to see if it's processing tasks:","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"The task is still PENDING - no `.executing` marker, no progress. It's now been 2h 18m since the task was created.\n\nLet me check if the heartbeat master daemon is processing tasks or if there are any logs about this:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a703f31e7d754c96b659460b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la ~/.openclaw/agents/main/logs/ 2>/dev/null | head -10"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2a05a7c797b14143b003d45b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"tail -30 ~/.openclaw/agents/main/logs/heartbeat-master.log 2>/dev/null || echo \"No heartbeat-master.log\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":29334,"output":1084,"cacheRead":3392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33810,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772703131119}}
