ve been dispatched and executed ✓\n4. No pending critical issues ✓\n\nI should still check:\n1. Are there any new pending tasks?\n2. Is there anything that needs attention?\n\nLet me check if there are any remaining pending tasks.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"**EXCELLENT NEWS!**\n\nLooking at the task-watcher-state.json, I can see that after the restart at 05:03:09, the task-watcher executed ALL pending tasks:\n\n| Task | Executed | Status |\n|------|----------|--------|\n| `temujin/high-1772694499.parse-for-agents-vision-a.md` | 05:03:10 | ✅ SUCCESS |\n| `ogedei/high-error-spike-investigation.md` | 05:03:10 | ✅ SUCCESS |\n| `jochi/auto-20260304-2302-router-audit.md` | 05:03:09 | ✅ SUCCESS |\n| `chagatai/auto-20260304-2208-incident-cron-failures.md` | 05:03:09 | ✅ SUCCESS |\n| `mongke/auto-20260304-2208-parse-competitor-pricing.md` | 05:03:10 | ✅ SUCCESS |\n| `temujin/heartbeat-review-20260303-015632.md` | 05:03:22 | ✅ SUCCESS |\n| `ogedei/auto-20260304-2208-scrapling-verification.md` | 05:03:22 | ✅ SUCCESS |\n\n**The HIGH priority task for Temujin was successfully executed at 05:03:10!**\n\nThe task files now show `.in_progress.done.md` suffix, indicating they were processed.\n\nLet me check if there are any remaining pending tasks:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b062f5985c194fc1b1d2b897","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"for agent in temujin mongke chagatai jochi ogedei kublai; do\n  count=$(ls ~/.openclaw/agents/$agent/tasks/*.md 2>/dev/null | grep -v \".completed.done\" | grep -v \".in_progress.done\" | grep -v \".executing\" | wc -l | tr -d ' ')\n  if [ \"$count\" -gt 0 ]; then\n    echo \"$agent: $count pending\"\n    ls ~/.openclaw/agents/$agent/tasks/*.md 2>/dev/null | grep -v \".completed.done\" | grep -v \".in_progress.done\" | grep -v \".executing\"\n  fi\ndone"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":2651,"output":1104,"cacheRead":56960,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60715,"cost":{"inpu