{"type":"message","id":"43b953a8","parentId":"583cccc3","timestamp":"2026-03-05T10:33:50.643Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! The heartbeat check at 5:31 AM shows:\n\n1. **Infrastructure:**\n   - Parse: 200 ✅\n   - LLM Survivor: 200 ✅\n\n2. **Watchdog log:**\n   - New entries at 05:19, 05:23, 05:25, 05:30 - the cron is running properly now!\n   - status=healthy ✅\n   - tasks_pending=0 ✅ (my fix worked - all tasks executed, no pending)\n   - tasks_dispatched=0 ✅\n   - errors=2 (low, acceptable)\n   - neo4j=up, redis=up ✅\n\n3. **Subagents:**\n   - None active/recent ✅\n\n4. **No critical escalations or blocked agents**\n\nThe system is now healthy and running properly. The path fix I made earlier is confirmed working:\n- tasks_pending went from 2 to 0\n- The watchdog is running every 5 minutes as expected\n- New log entries are being generated at 05:19, 05:23, 05:25, 05:30\n\nThis is exactly what we wanted to see after the fix.\n\nFor the heartbeat response:\n- Infrastructure: HEALTHY\n- All issues resolved\n- System running normally\n- No pending tasks\n- No urgent issues\n\nI should respond with HEARTBEAT_OK.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! The heartbeat check shows everything is working properly now:\n\n**Infrastructure:**\n- Parse: 200 ✅\n- LLM Survivor: 200 ✅\n\n**Watchdog Log (confirming the fix worked):**\n```\n[2026-03-05 05:25:00] TICK | status=healthy | tasks_pending=0 | neo4j=up | redis=up\n[2026-03-05 05:30:01] TICK | status=healthy | tasks_pending=0 | neo4j=up | redis=up\n```\n\nThe watchdog is now running every 5 minutes with:\n- status=healthy ✅\n- tasks_pending=0 ✅ (confirmed - my path fix worked!)\n- neo4j=up, redis=up ✅\n- errors=2 (low, acceptable)\n\n**Subagents:** None stuck ✅\n\n---\n\n**Summary:**\n- All infrastructure healthy\n- Path fix from earlier confirmed working (tasks_pending now correctly shows 0)\n- Watchdog cron running normally\n- No pending tasks\n- No critical issues\n\nHEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":70061,"output":525,"cacheRead":1600,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72186,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772706800748}}
