{"type":"message","id":"273ecea3","parentId":"49f475dc","timestamp":"2026-03-05T11:01:47.261Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Another heartbeat poll at 6:01 AM. Looking at HEARTBEAT.md:\n\n## Deep Reflection Hours: 0, 6, 12, 18 (every 6 hours)\n\nCurrent time is 6:01 AM - this IS a deep reflection hour!\n\nAccording to HEARTBEAT.md:\n\n## Deep Reflection (Every 6 Hours — Hours 0,6,12,18)\n\n**Complete these during your deep reflection hours:**\n\n### Self-Awareness\n- [ ] Review ARCHITECTURE.md for accuracy\n- [ ] Check Change Log is up to date\n- [ ] Verify all agent workspaces are correct\n\n### Git & Version Control\n- [ ] Commit any uncommitted changes\n- [ ] Push to GitHub if needed\n- [ ] Update Change Log with major changes\n\n### Coordination\n- [ ] Check all agent statuses\n- [ ] Resolve any blockers\n- [ ] Reprioritize task queue if needed\n\n### Strategic\n- [ ] Review progress toward goals\n- [ ] Identify opportunities\n- [ ] Plan next 6 hours\n\nSo at 6:01 AM, I need to do the DEEP REFLECTION, not just the quick check.\n\nLet me do the deep reflection now.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Heartbeat at 6:01 AM - this is a **DEEP REFLECTION HOUR** (hours 0, 6, 12, 18).\n\nPer HEARTBEAT.md, I need to complete the Deep Reflection checklist in addition to the quick check. Let me start:\n\n## Quick Check First"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d37112ce52714cadb7a8e69d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" https://www.parsethe.media && echo \"\" && curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" https://llmsurvivor.kurult.ai/"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_62b68af9e17448ad92085e12","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"tail -5 ~/.openclaw/agents/main/logs/watchdog.log 2>/dev/null"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0467ac555a0d440785fefcc7","name":"subagents","arguments":{"action":"list","recentMinutes":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5