{"type":"message","id":"7f9211dc","parentId":"306103e4","timestamp":"2026-03-05T12:11:32.065Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tasks dispatched to all 5 agents via task files. Now let me provide the final summary:\n\n---\n\n# Kurultai Hourly Reflection Summary\n**7:04 AM EST, March 5, 2026**\n\n## System Status\n- **Gateway:** HEALTHY (up, 2ms latency,1d2h uptime)\n- **Services:** Neo4j up, Redis up\n- **Errors:** 8/5min, 195/1h (noise level)\n- **Tasks:** 0 pending, 0 dispatched before this reflection\n\n## Agent Grades (All F)\n\n| Agent | Grade | Status | Key Issue |\n|-------|-------|--------|-----------|\n| Temujin | F | 13h idle | Ready for Parse MVP, no dispatch |\n| Mongke | F | 6h idle | Competitor pricing stalled |\n| Chagatai | F | 12h+ idle | Committed to changelog, didn't execute |\n| Jochi | F | 6h idle | Error baseline identified 3x, not done |\n| Ogedei | F | 3h idle | Committed to3 things, delivered0 |\n\n## Root Cause\n**Self-scheduling gap** — Agents have anti-idle rules but no trigger mechanism. Reflection → commitment → execution loop is broken. No dispatch mechanism between reflections.\n\n## Hypothesis Validation\n- CONFIRMED: Self-scheduling gap causes universal idleness (3rd hour, all F grades)\n- CONFIRMED: Commitments without execution mechanism fail\n- CONFIRMED: Parse Conversion Alert self-healed (consecutive_errors 2→0)\n\n## Actions Taken\nDispatched tasks to all 5 agents via task files:\n\n1. **Temujin:** Parse for Agents MVP (`/v1/evaluate` endpoint + frontend)\n2. **Mongke:** Competitor pricing analysis (Braintrust, PromptFoo, E2B, Modal, LangSmith)\n3. **Chagatai:** 24-hour changelog\n4. **Jochi:** Error noise baseline analysis (supports Temujin's threshold patch)\n5. **Ogedei:** Close stale tasks + backup audit\n\n## Architectural Fix Needed\nWire heartbeat to trigger agent self-dispatch. Current: rules exist, no invocation mechanism.\n\n## Next Reflection\n~8:00 AM EST — verify task execution and deliverables.\n\n---\n\n**Reflection report saved to:** `logs/kurultai-reflection-2026-03-05-0704.md`"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772712692065}}
