{"type":"message","id":"f33e59cc","parentId":"eec199db","timestamp":"2026-03-05T14:08:21.420Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user (Danny) is saying \"Test it\". This is a direct message from the human operator, not a heartbeat poll.\n\nLooking at the context:\n- This is Danny, the human operator\n- They're saying \"Test it\"\n- This is at 9:07 AM EST on March 5, 2026\n\nI need to understand what \"Test it\" refers to. Looking at the recent context:\n\n1. I fixed a path bug earlier today in the task execution scripts\n2. There was a HIGH priority task for Temujin: \"Build Vision A of Parse for Agents\"\n3. That task was executed at 05:03:10 according to the task-watcher-state.json\n4. The task was about building a prompt testing sandbox API\n\nThe \"Test it\" message is likely referring to testing the Parse for Agents feature that Temujin was supposed to build. Let me check what the task deliverables were supposed to be:\n\nFrom the task I read earlier (high-1772694499.parse-for-agents-vision-a.md):\n- Frontend URL: http://localhost:3000/agents\n- API endpoints: /api/v1/evaluate, etc.\n- Success criteria: Can submit a prompt via frontend UI and see results\n\nSo Danny wants me to test the Parse for Agents feature. Let me check if it's running and accessible.\n\nI should:\n1. Check if the Parse frontend is accessible at /agents\n2. Check if the API endpoints are working\n3. Report the results to Danny\n\nThis is NOT a heartbeat - this is a direct request from the human. I should NOT reply with HEARTBEAT_OK.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Danny wants me to test something. Given the context, this is likely referring to the \"Parse for Agents\" feature that Temujin was building - the HIGH priority task that was executed earlier this morning.\n\nLet me test the Parse for Agents frontend and API endpoints."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8a9141f99d0447c2ad4af56d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" https://www.parsethe.media/agents"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_67c192fdcc4f43029fc6fd3f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s https://www.parsethe.media/api/v1/agents-test/models 2>/dev/null | head -50"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_399760c05150468fa0dcc5bb","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s https://www.parsethe.media/api/v1/agents-test/evaluators 2>/dev/null | head -50"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":94376,"output":501,"cacheRead":3392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98269,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772719678154}}
