{"type":"message","id":"7f09af49","parentId":"fea31a18","timestamp":"2026-03-05T14:08:42.229Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The test results show:\n\n1. **/agents page**: Returns 404 - \"This page could not be found\"\n2. **/api/v1/agents-test/models**: Returns 404 HTML page\n3. **/api/v1/agents-test/evaluators**: Returns 404 HTML page\n\nThis means the \"Parse for Agents\" feature has NOT been built or deployed. The task that was marked as \"executed successfully\" in the task-watcher-state.json didn't actually build the feature.\n\nLet me check what happened with the task. I should look at the task result file or check if there's any output from the execution.\n\nThe task was `temujin/high-1772694499.parse-for-agents-vision-a.md` and it was marked as \"success: true\" in the state file. But the feature doesn't exist on the live site.\n\nI should:\n1. Check if the task file has any results logged\n2. Report to Danny that the feature is not available\n3. Investigate what happened with the task execution\n\nLet me check the task file for any results.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"The test results show that the **Parse for Agents** feature is NOT available:\n\n| Endpoint | Result |\n|----------|--------|\n| `/agents` | 404 - Page not found |\n| `/api/v1/agents-test/models` | 404 - Page not found |\n| `/api/v1/agents-test/evaluators` | 404 - Page not found |\n\nThe feature was NOT built or deployed. Let me check what happened with the task execution:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_317bfce0d3eb4cb88af04c20","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la ~/.openclaw/agents/temujin/tasks/*parse-for-agents* 2>/dev/null"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_22b1a7e52cf6441e897848a6","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/agents/temujin/tasks/high-1772694499.parse-for-agents-vision-a.in_progress.done.md 2>/dev/null | head -50"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"