{"type":"message","id":"887da402","parentId":"7f09af49","timestamp":"2026-03-05T14:08:42.246Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_317bfce0d3eb4cb88af04c20","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"-rw-r--r--  1 kublai  staff  2916 Mar  5 02:13 /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/temujin/tasks/high-1772694499.parse-for-agents-vision-a.in_progress.done.md\n-rw-r--r--  1 kublai  staff   760 Mar  5 07:10 /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/temujin/tasks/high-1772713500-parse-for-agents-mvp.in_progress.done.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":7,"aggregated":"-rw-r--r--  1 kublai  staff  2916 Mar  5 02:13 /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/temujin/tasks/high-1772694499.parse-for-agents-vision-a.in_progress.done.md\n-rw-r--r--  1 kublai  staff   760 Mar  5 07:10 /Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/temujin/tasks/high-1772713500-parse-for-agents-mvp.in_progress.done.md","cwd":"/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772719722243}}
{"type":"message","id":"41ace3bb","parentId":"887da402","timestamp":"2026-03-05T14:08:42.261Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_22b1a7e52cf6441e897848a6","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# TASK: Build Vision A of Parse for Agents\n\n**Priority:** HIGH\n**Created:** 2026-03-05 02:08 EST\n**Assigned by:** Kublai\n**Status:** PENDING\n\n---\n\n## Objective\n\nBuild a complete, polished \"Vision A\" of Parse for Agents - a prompt testing sandbox API. Deliver a working frontend URL for Danny to test.\n\n---\n\n## Context\n\nParse for Agents is a prompt testing sandbox API that lets developers test, evaluate, and benchmark LLM prompts. \n\n**Spec Files:**\n- ~/projects/parse-github/PARSE_FOR_AGENTS.md\n- ~/projects/parse-github/SPEC-parse-for-agents.md\n\n**Note:** A basic MVP was built earlier. Your job is to build \"Vision A\" properly - the complete, polished version with all features working.\n\n---\n\n## Deliverables\n\n### 1. Core API Endpoints\n- `POST /api/v1/evaluate` - Submit prompt evaluation (returns 202 with job ID)\n- `GET /api/v1/evaluate/[id]` - Poll for results\n- `GET /api/v1/agents-test/models` - List supported models\n- `GET /api/v1/agents-test/evaluators` - List available evaluators\n- API key authentication working\n\n### 2. Evaluators (Must Work)\n- **Cost** - Token counting, pricing per model\n- **Latency** - Timing, tokens per second\n- **Quality** - LLM-as-judge using OpenAI (gpt-4o-mini) or DeepSeek\n\n### 3. Frontend at /agents\n- Prompt template editor with `{{input}}` interpolation\n- Model selector (multiple providers)\n- Evaluator checkboxes (quality, cost, latency)\n- Temperature/max tokens configuration\n- Real-time polling for results\n- Results display:\n  - Quality scores with sub-score breakdown\n  - Cost metrics (tokens, USD)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":5,"aggregated":"# TASK: Build Vision A of Parse for Agents\n\n**Priority:** HIGH\n**Created:** 2026-03-05 02:08 EST\n**Assigned by:** Kublai\n**Status:** PENDING\n\n---\n\n## Objective\n\nBuild a complete, polished \"Vision A\" of Parse for Agents - a prompt testing sandbox API. Deliver a working frontend URL for Danny to test.\n\n---\n\n## Context\n\nParse for Agents is a prompt testing sandbox API that lets developers test, evaluate, and benchmark LLM prompts. \n\n**Spec Files:**\n- ~/projects/parse-github/PARSE_FOR_AGENTS.md\n- ~/projects/parse-github/SPEC-parse-for-agents.md\n\n**Note:** A basic MVP was built earlier. Your job is to build \"Vision A\" properly - the complete, polished version with all features working.\n\n---\n\n## Deliverables\n\n### 1. Core API Endpoints\n- `POST /api/v1/evaluate` - Submit prompt evaluation (returns 202 with job ID)\n- `GET /api/v1/evaluate/[id]` - Poll for results\n- `GET /api/v1/agents-test/models` - List supported models\n- `GET /api/v1/agents-test/evaluators` - List available evaluators\n- API key authentication working\n\n### 2. Evaluators (Must Work)\n- **Cost** - Token counting, pricing per model\n- **Latency** - Timing, tokens per second\n- **Quality** - LLM-as-judge using OpenAI (gpt-4o-mini) or DeepSeek\n\n### 3. Frontend at /agents\n- Prompt template editor with `{{input}}` interpolation\n- Model selector (multiple providers)\n- Evaluator checkboxes (quality, cost, latency)\n- Temperature/max tokens configuration\n- Real-time polling for results\n- Results display:\n  - Quality scores with sub-score breakdown\n  - Cost metrics (tokens, USD)","cwd":"/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772719722255}}
{"type":"message","id":"896a9321","parentId":"41ace3bb","timestamp":"2026-03-05T14:09:03.775Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The task file shows the task definition but it was just marked as \".in_progress.done.md\" - there's no actual result logged. The task was marked as \"done\" but the feature wasn't actually built.\n\nThis is a problem - the task-watcher marked the task as successful but didn't actually execute the work. Let me check the task-watcher log to see what happened during the execution.\n\nActually, looking at this more carefully:\n1. The task file `high-1772694499.parse-for-agents-vision-a.md` was created at 02:08 EST\n2. The task-watcher executed it at 05:03:10 according to the state file\n3. The task was marked as \"success: true\"\n4. But the feature doesn't exist on the live site\n\nThis suggests that when the task-watcher \"executed\" the task, it might have just read the file and marked it as done without actually doing the work. Or maybe it spawned a subagent that failed silently.\n\nLet me check the task-watcher log to see what happened.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"The task file shows the task definition but there's no result logged. The task was marked as \"done\" but the feature wasn't actually built. Let me check the task-watcher log to see what happened during execution:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2943e512e5684155b9038177","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -A5 \"parse-for-agents-vision-a\" ~/.openclaw/agents/main/logs/task-watcher.log 2>/dev/null"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_792de75944bf494e984516c0","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/agents/main/logs/task-watcher.log 2>/dev/null | grep -A10 \"05:03:\" | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":113401,"output":349,"cacheRead":64,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113814,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"st