{"type":"message","id":"8d431e69","parentId":"bcae1457","timestamp":"2026-03-05T15:08:24.861Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Looking at the results:\n\n1. **Task files in Temujin's directory:**\n   - `high-1772694499.parse-for-agents-vision-a.in_progress.done.md` - original task\n   - `high-1772713500-parse-for-agents-mvp.in_progress.done.md` - another task from 07:10\n   - `high-1772722500-parse-for-agents-build.in_progress.done.md` - **MY NEW TASK** (created at 09:55)\n\n2. **Task-watcher state shows:**\n   - Most recent execution was `high-1772713500-parse-for-agents-mvp.md` at 09:53:05\n\nThe task file I created (`high-1772722500-parse-for-agents-build.md`) has been renamed to `.in_progress.done.md` - which means it was picked up and marked as done. But was it actually executed? Let me check the full state:"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772723304861}}
{"type":"message","id":"b4062f17","parentId":"8d431e69","timestamp":"2026-03-05T15:08:24.938Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Found it. Here's the status:\n\n**Task Execution Status:**\n\n| Task | Executed | Success |\n|------|----------|---------|\n| `temujin/high-1772722500-parse-for-agents-build.md` | 09:53:34 | True |\n\n**The problem:** The task was marked as \"success\" but the feature STILL doesn't exist. Let me verify:"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772723304938}}
{"type":"message","id":"ca331309","parentId":"b4062f17","timestamp":"2026-03-05T15:08:24.999Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Temujin Status - PROBLEM IDENTIFIED**\n\n| Check | Result |\n|-------|--------|\n| Task executed? | Yes - 09:53:34 |\n| Marked success? | Yes - True |\n| Feature built? | **NO** - Still 404 |\n\n**The task execution system is broken.** Tasks are being marked as \"success\" without any actual work being done.\n\n**What's happening:**\n1. Task-watcher picks up the task\n2. Spawns an agent session with `openclaw agent --agent temujin`\n3. Agent acknowledges the task\n4. System marks it as \"success\"\n5. **But no actual Claude Code execution happens** - no code is written, no deployment occurs\n\n**Root cause:** The task execution system doesn't actually invoke Claude Code to build things. It just has the agent \"read and acknowledge\" the task, which counts as success.\n\n**The feature at `/agents` still returns 404** despite multiple tasks being marked as \"success.\"\n\n**What needs to happen:** Someone (Danny or a human) needs to actually run Claude Code directly to build this feature. The automated task execution system cannot currently execute coding work - it only acknowledges tasks."}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772723304999}}
{"type":"message","id":"f086980d","parentId":"33d1f9b8","timestamp":"2026-03-05T15:08:58.716Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is sending another heartbeat poll. Current time is Thursday, March 5th, 2026 — 10:08 AM (America/New_York).\n\nI just finished responding to a status check about whether Temujin is working. I found that:\n1. The task execution system is broken\n2. Tasks are marked as \"success\" without actual work being done\n3. The Parse for Agents feature still doesn't exist (404)\n\nNow I'm getting a heartbeat poll. This is NOT a deep reflection hour (those are at 0, 6, 12, 18).\n\nI should do the quick infrastructure check per HEARTBEAT.md.\n\nBut wait - I just identified a critical issue with the task execution system. Is this \"something that needs attention\"?\n\nLooking at HEARTBEAT.md:\n- \"If Something Needs Attention: Report what's blocked, which agent is affected, what decision/action is needed\"\n- \"If nothing urgent → respond `HEARTBEAT_OK`\"\n\nThe task execution system being broken is definitely something that needs attention. But I already reported this in my response to the \"is temujin still working\" question. The issue is now documented.\n\nFor the heartbeat:\n- Infrastructure is healthy (Parse main site works, LLM Survivor works)\n- The task execution issue is known and reported\n- No new issues\n\nI should do the quick check and if everything is healthy, respond HEARTBEAT_OK.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Another heartbeat poll at 10:08 AM. I just finished investigating and reporting on the Temujin task execution issue.\n\nThis is NOT a deep reflection hour (those are at 0, 6, 12, 18).\n\nLet me do the quick infrastructure check per HEARTBEAT.md."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_91e2da94928b40b78b372478","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" https://www.parsethe.media && echo \"\" && curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" http