------|--------|----------|\n| **Parse Monetization** | Active | Injection detection spec added today; /agents still 404 |\n| **LLM Survivor** | Live | Healthy, monitoring |\n| **Heartbeat Daemon** | Running | Path bug fixed today, system healthy |\n\n### Key Accomplishments Today (2026-03-05):\n1. **Fixed critical path bug** in task execution scripts (watchdog-gather.sh, heartbeat-task-executor.py, task-watcher.py)\n2. **Verified task execution** - Temujin successfully updated Parse spec with injection detection evaluator\n3. **Researched competitors** - Grith.ai (runtime security), Brainworm (promptware)\n4. **Installed Google Cloud SDK** for Kublai's Google Workspace setup (OAuth pending)\n\n### Issues to Track:\n1. Git push credentials not configured\n2. MEMORY.md needs updating\n3. Parse for Agents /agents endpoint still returns 404\n4. Google Workspace OAuth authentication pending\n\n### Next 6 Hours Plan (12:07 PM - 6:07 PM):\n1. Monitor task queue execution\n2. Verify Parse for Agents deployment status\n3. Complete Google Workspace OAuth (requires manual intervention)\n4. Update MEMORY.md with current status\n5. Continue heartbeat monitoring\n\n---\n\n**System Status: HEALTHY**\n- All infrastructure operational\n- Task execution system working after path fix\n- 12 pending tasks in queue\n\nHEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":3670,"output":776,"cacheRead":133120,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137566,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772730477086}}
