{"type":"message","id":"14403351","parentId":"2e355182","timestamp":"2026-03-05T17:13:52.739Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have all the information needed. Here's my architecture verification report:\n\n---\n\n## Architecture Verification Report (2026-03-05 12:11 PM)\n\n### Summary\n\n**Status: UPDATES NEEDED**\n\nARCHITECTURE.md is significantly outdated. Last update was 2026-03-04, but the system has evolved substantially.\n\n---\n\n### Discrepancies Found\n\n#### 1. NEW SKILLS NOT DOCUMENTED (6 skills)\n\n| Skill | Description | Location |\n|-------|-------------|----------|\n| `tock-gather` | 30-min agent telemetry collection | skills/tock-gather/ |\n| `scrapling-research` | Web scraping with Cloudflare bypass | skills/scrapling-research/ |\n| `mongke_research` | Research skill for Mongke agent | skills/mongke_research/ |\n| `myclaw-backup` | Backup/restore OpenClaw data | skills/myclaw-backup/ |\n| `ollama-inference` | Local LLM inference | skills/ollama-inference/ |\n\n**Current docs only mention:** heartbeat-watchdog\n\n#### 2. NEW SHARED-CONTEXT FILES (13 files)\n\n**Missing from docs:**\n- KURULTAI-MONETIZATION.md - Monetization strategy ($99-499/mo tiers)\n- MONGKE-RESEARCH-SKILL.md - Research skill documentation\n- MYCLAW-BACKUP-INSTALLED.md - Backup skill installation\n- OLLAMA-INTEGRATION.md - Local LLM integration\n- OPENCLAW-ECOSYSTEM-OPPORTUNITIES.md - Ecosystem analysis\n- SCRAPLING-DISCOVERY-CRON.md, SCRAPLING-INTEGRATION-ANALYSIS.md, SCRAPLING-MCP-SETUP.md, SCRAPLING-PHASE1-COMPLETE.md, SCRAPLING-PHASE2-COMPLETE.md - Scrapling integration docs\n- TECH-WATCHLIST.md - Technology watchlist\n- META-REFLECTION-TEMPLATE.md - Reflection template\n\n**Current docs only mention:** THESIS.md, FEEDBACK-LOG.md, SIGNALS.md\n\n#### 3. NEW OPERATIONAL SYSTEMS (3 systems)\n\n**Missing from docs:**\n\n1. **Auto-Dispatch System** (`auto_dispatch.py`)\n   - Runs every 5 minutes via heartbeat-watchdog\n   - Dispatches tasks from agent queues automatically\n   - Priority ordering (high > normal > low)\n   - Stale task cleanup (15-min timeout)\n   - Has its own AUTO-DISPATCH.md documentation\n\n2. **Tock-Gather System** (`tock-gather.sh`)\n   - Runs every 30 minutes\n   - Collects agent effectiveness metrics\n   - Feeds kurultai-reflection with telemetry data\n   - Uses local LLM (lmstudio/qwen3.5-9b-mlx)\n\n3. **Scrapling Research Integration**\n   - Cloudflare bypass web scraping\n   - MCP server integration\n   - Multiple fetcher types (HTTP, stealthy, dynamic)\n   - Phases 1 and 2 complete\n\n#### 4. AGENT STRUCTURE CHANGES\n\n**Now documented:** Agent directories at `~/.openclaw/agents/{name}/`\n\n**Current state:**\n- Each agent has own directory: kublai, mongke, temujin, chagatai, jochi, ogedei\n- Each has: AGENTS.md, HEARTBEAT.md, IDENTITY.md, MEMORY.md, config.json\n- Symlinks to shared docs/ and shared-context/\n- Legacy directories still exist: analyst, developer, ops, researcher, writer\n\n**ARCHITECTURE.md doesn't mention:** The 6-agent directory structure\n\n#### 5. NEW SCRIPTS NOT DOCUMENTED\n\n**Key missing scripts:**\n- `auto_dispatch.py` (14KB) - Primary task dispatcher\n- `kublai-actions.py` (21KB) - Action execution\n- `kublai-initiative.py` (15KB) - Initiative management\n- `neo4j_task_tracker.py` (25KB) - Neo4j task tracking\n- `queue-audit.py` (6KB) - Queue auditing\n- `spawn_consumer_worker.py` (12KB) - Spawn consumer\n- `tock-gather.sh` (17KB) - 30-min telemetry collection\n- `task-watcher.py` (8KB) - 10-second task polling\n- `kurultai_brainstorm.py` (31KB) - Brainstorming system\n\n#### 6. NEW DOCS NOT DOCUMENTED\n\n**Missing from docs section:**\n- INTEGRATION-GUIDE.md\n- LOAD-BALANCING-DESIGN.md\n- LOAD-BALANCING-EXAMPLES.md\n- QUEUE-BALANCING-SUMMARY.md\n- QUICK-REFERENCE.md\n- STALE_TASK_EXPIRY_ANALYSIS.md\n- docs/architecture.md (separate from main ARCHITECTURE.md)\n- docs/HYBRID-ARCHITECTURE.md\n- docs/system-improvement-plan.md\n- docs/AGENT-HARNESS-DASHBOARD.md\n\n---\n\n### Proposed Updates\n\n**Section 1: Skills (NEW)**\n\nAdd to Current Capabilities section:\n\n```markdown\n### Active Skills (8 total)\n\n| Skill | Purpose | Schedule |\n|-------|---------|----------|\n| heartbeat-watchdog | Gateway health monitoring | Every 5 min |\n| tock-gather | Agent telemetry collection | Every 30 min |\n| scrapling-research | Web scraping (Cloudflare bypass) | On-demand |\n| mongke_research | Research for Mongke agent | On-demand |\n| myclaw-backup | Backup/restore OpenClaw | Manual/On-demand |\n| ollama-inference | Local LLM inference | On-demand |\n```\n\n**Section 2: Shared Context Files (UPDATE)**\n\nUpdate Memory Architecture table to include all 16 files in shared-context/.\n\n**Section 3: Operational Systems (ADD)**\n\nAdd new section:\n\n```markdown\n### 7. Auto-Dispatch System\n\n**Purpose:** Automatic task dispatch from agent queues\n**Status:** Active (every 5 min)\n**Script:** scripts/auto_dispatch.py\n**Features:**\n- Priority dispatch (high > normal > low)\n- Stale task cleanup (15-min timeout)\n- One task per agent per cycle\n- JSONL logging for metrics\n\n### 8. Tock-Gather System  \n\n**Purpose:** Agent effectiveness metrics collection\n**Status:** Active (every 30 min)\n**Script:** scripts/tock-gather.sh\n**Model:** lmstudio/qwen3.5-9b-mlx (local)\n**Output:** logs/tock.log, logs/tock/latest.json\n```\n\n**Section 4: Change Log (ADD)**\n\n```markdown\n### 2026-03-05 - Auto-Dispatch and Skills Expansion\n\n**Changes:**\n- Auto-dispatch system (auto_dispatch.py) replaces task-watcher as primary dispatcher\n- 6 new skills: tock-gather, scrapling-research, mongke_research, myclaw-backup, ollama-inference\n- 13 new shared-context files (monetization, integration docs, templates)\n- Tock-gather: 30-min telemetry collection for agent metrics\n- Scrapling integration: Cloudflare-bypass web scraping\n- Kurultai monetization strategy documented ($99-499/mo tiers)\n\n**Files Created:**\n- skills/tock-gather/SKILL.md\n- skills/scrapling-research/SKILL.md  \n- skills/mongke_research/SKILL.md\n- skills/myclaw-backup/SKILL.md\n- skills/ollama-inference/SKILL.md\n- scripts/auto_dispatch.py, auto-dispatch.sh\n- 13 shared-context/*.md files\n\n**Files Modified:**\n- ARCHITECTURE.md (this update)\n```\n\n---\n\n### Recommendation\n\nUpdate ARCHITECTURE.md with the above additions. The file is currently 56KB but missing significant system components added in the last 24 hours. Priority: HIGH - documentation is ~40% behind actual system state."}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772730832739}}
