{"type":"message","id":"ef5d0da7","parentId":"59e7dd60","timestamp":"2026-03-05T18:08:13.228Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! The user is asking me to bring Parse for Agents to production readiness. This is a direct instruction from the human operator.\n\nThe quick check shows:\n\n1. **Code exists:**\n   - `/src/app/agents/page.tsx` - 24696 bytes, modified Mar 5 12:29\n   - `/src/app/agents-test/page.tsx` - 19130 bytes, modified Mar 5 01:42\n   - `/src/app/api/v1/agents-test/` - directory exists\n   - `/src/app/api/v1/evaluate/` - directory exists\n\n2. **Production status:**\n   - `/agents` returns 200! ✅ (this changed from earlier!)\n   - `/api/v1/evaluate` returns 405 (Method Not Allowed - endpoint exists but needs POST)\n\nWait - this is different from earlier today! Earlier I tested `/agents` and it returned 404. Now it returns 200!\n\nLet me verify this more thoroughly. The feature might actually be partially deployed now.\n\nLet me check:\n1. What the /agents page looks like\n2. What the /api/v1/agents-test endpoints return\n3. What still needs to be done for production readiness\n\nActually, looking at the codebase:\n- `/src/app/agents/page.tsx` exists (24696 bytes)\n- `/src/app/agents-test/page.tsx` exists (19130 bytes)\n- API endpoints exist under `/src/app/api/v1/`\n\nThe feature appears to be built! Let me verify the production status more thoroughly.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Excellent news! The quick check shows that progress has been made:\n\n**Current Status:**\n\n| Endpoint | Code | Status |\n|----------|------|--------|\n| `/agents` | **200** ✅ | Frontend EXISTS! |\n| `/api/v1/evaluate` | 405 | Endpoint exists (needs POST) |\n\nThe code also shows:\n- `/src/app/agents/page.tsx` - 24696 bytes (modified Mar 5 12:29)\n- `/src/app/agents-test/page.tsx` - 19130 bytes (modified Mar 5 01:42)\n- API directories: `agents-test/`, `evaluate/`, `agents/`\n\n**This is different from earlier!** The `/agents` endpoint now returns 200 instead of 404. Someone has been working on this.\n\nLet me do a more thorough assessment of what's working and what still needs to be done for production readiness:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a58e69849d9744a0b7edbb83","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s https://www.parsethe.media/api/v1/agents-test/models 2>/dev/null | head -100"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_327ddc588fc84d9f9fa6b34d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s https://www.parsethe.media/api/v1/agents-test/evaluators 2>/dev/null | head -100"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c9604e38655642cfb7b91142","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X POST https://www.parsethe.media/api/v1/evaluate -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{}' 2>/dev/null | head -100"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":102301,"output":645,"cacheRead":44800,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":147746,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772734067392}}
