{"type":"message","id":"cf54aaa1","parentId":"cf5d6b56","timestamp":"2026-03-05T18:11:25.533Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The quick check results show:\n\n1. Infrastructure:\n   - Parse: 200 ✅\n   - LLM Survivor: 200 ✅\n\n2. Watchdog log (most recent at 13:08:29):\n   - status=healthy ✅ (recovered from degraded!)\n   - errors=50 (down from 51)\n   - tasks_pending=0\n   - neo4j=up, redis=up ✅\n   - action=none, reason=all checks passed ✅\n\nThe system has recovered from \"degraded\" back to \"healthy\"! The error count dropped from 51 to 50, which is back below the threshold.\n\nEverything is healthy now. I should respond with HEARTBEAT_OK.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"The quick check results show:\n\n1. Infrastructure:\n   - Parse: 200 ✅\n   - LLM Survivor: 200 ✅\n\n2. Watchdog log (most recent at 13:08:29):\n   - **status=healthy** ✅ (recovered from degraded!)\n   - errors=50 (down from 51)\n   - tasks_pending=0\n   - neo4j=up, redis=up ✅\n   - action=none, reason=all checks passed ✅\n\nThe system has recovered from \"degraded\" back to \"healthy\"! The error count dropped from 51 to 50.\n\n**Good news from earlier investigation:**\n- Parse for Agents is FULLY BUILT AND FUNCTIONAL\n- Frontend UI at /agents working\n- API endpoints working (models, evaluators, evaluate)\n- 9 models available with pricing\n- 4 evaluators including injection_safety\n\nEverything is healthy. I should respond with HEARTBEAT_OK.Quick check results at 1:10 PM:\n\n**Infrastructure:**\n- Parse: 200 ✅\n- LLM Survivor: 200 ✅\n\n**Watchdog Log (13:08:29):**\n```\nstatus=healthy | errors=50 | tasks_pending=0 | neo4j=up | redis=up\naction=none | reason=all checks passed\n```\n\n**Status:**\n- System recovered from \"degraded\" to \"healthy\" ✅\n- errors=50 (down from 51, below threshold)\n- All infrastructure healthy\n- No urgent issues\n\nHEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"i