{"type":"message","id":"1bad209d","parentId":"95e6d499","timestamp":"2026-03-05T19:14:51.322Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user said \"you should have access to parse now\" and I'm now at the Google OAuth consent screen for Parse. The page shows:\n\n1. \"Sign in with Google\"\n2. \"Sign in to parsethe.media\"\n3. \"kublai@kurult.ai selected. Switch account\"\n4. \"Google will allow parsethe.media to access this info about you\"\n   - Name and profile picture: Kublai Kurultai\n   - Email address: kublai@kurult.ai\n5. \"Cancel\" and \"Continue\" buttons\n\nThis is the same consent screen I saw multiple times earlier. Every time I clicked \"Continue\", the OAuth flow would redirect back to the sign-in page without completing the authentication.\n\nThe user said \"you should have access to parse now\" - maybe they fixed the OAuth callback issue. Let me try clicking \"Continue\" again and see if it works this time.\n\nI've been through this flow multiple times already. Let me try clicking \"Continue\" one more time and see if the OAuth callback works now.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"The user said \"you should have access to parse now\" and I'm now at the Google OAuth consent screen for Parse. The page shows:\n\n1. \"Sign in to parsethe.media\"\n2. \"kublai@kurult.ai selected\"\n3. Google will allow parsethe.media to access:\n   - Name and profile picture: Kublai Kurultai\n   - Email address: kublai@kurult.ai\n4. \"Cancel\" and \"Continue\" buttons\n\nThis is the same consent screen I saw multiple times earlier. Every time I clicked \"Continue\", the OAuth flow would redirect back to the sign-in page without completing the authentication.\n\nThe user said \"you should have access to parse now\" - maybe they fixed the OAuth callback issue. Let me try clicking \"Continue\" again and see if it works this time.The user said \"you should have access to parse now\" and I'm now at the Google OAuth consent screen for Parse. The page shows:\n\n1. \"Sign in to parsethe.media\"\n2. \"kublai@kurult.ai selected\"\n3. Google will allow parsethe.media to access:\n   - Name and profile picture: Kublai Kurultai\n   - Email address: kublai@kurult.ai\n4. \"Cancel\" and \"Continue\" buttons\n\nThis is the same consent screen I saw multiple times earlier. Every time I clicked \"Continue\", the OAuth flow would redirect back to the sign-in page without completing the authentication.\n\nThe user said \"you should have access to parse now\" - maybe they fixed the OAuth callback issue. Let me try clicking \"Continue\" again and see if it works this time."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ccd6af4e9c724aa79869a4f9","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","kind":"click","ref":"e90","targetId":"6184D414BDEBCEA6CDA0EF9002734742"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":55634,"output":614,"cacheRead":99136,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":155384,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772738069565}}
