urrent Dispatch Status\n- **Dispatched at 16:09:13:** jochi/competitor-intel.md, mongke/news-feed.md\n- **Still Pending:** mongke/openclaw-discovery.md\n- **Fleet-wide idle BROKEN** after 10+ hours - tasks now flowing\n\n### Actions Required (Next Hour)\n| Priority | Action | Owner |\n|----------|--------|-------|\n| HIGH | Create Parse MVP task for Temujin | Kublai |\n| HIGH | Create ARCHITECTURE.md review task for Chagatai | Kublai |\n| MEDIUM | Create error audit task for Ogedei | Kublai |\n| MEDIUM | Standardize task creation paths | Temujin |\n\n### The Momentum Question\n**What do I want to do next?**\n1. Create Parse MVP task for Temujin (highest-priority dev item)\n2. Create ARCHITECTURE.md review task for Chagatai\n3. Monitor task execution to verify dispatch is working\n4. Create error audit task for Ogedei\n\n---\n\n**Reflection complete at 4:12 PM EST, March 5, 2026**\n**Report saved to:** `/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main/logs/kurultai-reflection-2026-03-05-1604.md`"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772745005756}}
