{"type":"message","id":"a1e00c70","parentId":"46c627a7","timestamp":"2026-03-05T21:57:53.358Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user signed in with the credentials:\n- Email: kublai@kurult.ai\n- Password: WH@JRB6V67Yue39EcBqt3t\n\nBut the sign-in FAILED with the error message: **\"Invalid email or password\"**\n\nThis is the same issue as before. The account was created earlier, but sign-in still fails with \"Invalid email or password\".\n\nThe user said \"you're now able to access parsethe.media\" but the sign-in is still failing.\n\nLooking at the snapshot:\n1. \"Sign in to Parse\" - \"Welcome back\"\n2. \"Continue with Google\" button\n3. \"Continue with Facebook\" button\n4. **\"Invalid email or password\"** - ERROR MESSAGE\n5. Email textbox shows \"kublai@kurult.ai\"\n6. Password textbox shows \"WH@JRB6V67Yue39EcBqt3t\"\n7. \"Sign in\" button\n\nThe same credentials that worked to CREATE the account are not working to SIGN IN. This is a persistent issue.\n\nI should try:\n1. Google OAuth again (since the Kublai Google account exists)\n2. Ask the user for clarification\n3. Try a different approach\n\nActually, the user said \"you're now able to access parsethe.media\" - maybe they meant I should use Google OAuth instead of email/password. Let me try the \"Continue with Google\" button.\n\nThe Kublai Google account (kublai@kurult.ai) exists and the Google OAuth flow gets to the consent screen, but then redirects back to the sign-in page without completing. Maybe the user fixed the OAuth callback?\n\nLet me try \"Continue with Google\" again.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"The sign-in failed with **\"Invalid email or password\"** again. This is the same issue as before.\n\nLooking at the snapshot:\n1. \"Sign in to Parse\" - \"Welcome back\"\n2. **\"Invalid email or password\"** - ERROR MESSAGE\n3. Email textbox shows \"kublai@kurult.ai\"\n4. Password textbox shows \"WH@JRB6V67Yue39EcBqt3t\"\n\nThe same credentials that worked to CREATE the account are not working to SIGN IN. This is a persistent issue.\n\nThe user said \"you're now able to access parsethe.media\" - maybe they meant I should use Google OAuth instead. Let me try \"Continue with Google\" with the Kublai Google account.The sign-in failed with **\"Invalid email or password\"** again. This is the same issue as before.\n\nThe user said \"you're now able to access parsethe.media\" - maybe they meant I should use Google OAuth instead. Let me try \"Continue with Google\" with the Kublai Google account:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_027d145f129347579c0c82f5","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","kind":"click","ref":"e30","targetId":"8AA06D80ED0C4408D80B8BED16205D20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1229,"output":619,"cacheRead":152960,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":154808,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772747853359}}
