{"type":"message","id":"f6067f51","parentId":"28555f94","timestamp":"2026-03-05T21:58:26.012Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user clicked \"Continue with Google\" on the Parse sign-in page and the snapshot shows the Google OAuth page opened. The page shows:\n\n1. \"Sign in with Google\"\n2. \"Choose an account to continue to parsethe.media\"\n3. Two account options:\n   - **Kublai Kurultai kublai@kurult.ai** (ref=e43) - This is the account the user created for me!\n   - Danny Finn danservfinn@gmail.com (ref=e51)\n4. \"Use another account\" option\n\nThis is the Google account chooser. The Kublai Google account is showing, which means Google recognizes the account.\n\nEarlier, the OAuth flow would get to the consent screen after clicking on the Kublai account, but then clicking \"Continue\" would redirect back to the sign-in page without completing the authentication.\n\nThe user said \"you're now able to access parsethe.media\" - maybe they fixed the OAuth callback issue. Let me try clicking on the Kublai account and see if the OAuth flow completes successfully this time.\n\nLet me click on the Kublai Kurultai account (ref=e43).","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"The user clicked \"Continue with Google\" on the Parse sign-in page and the Google OAuth page opened. The page shows:\n\n1. \"Sign in with Google\"\n2. \"Choose an account to continue to parsethe.media\"\n3. Two account options:\n   - **Kublai Kurultai kublai@kurult.ai** (ref=e43) - This is the account the user created for me!\n   - Danny Finn danservfinn@gmail.com (ref=e51)\n4. \"Use another account\" option\n\nThis is the Google account chooser. The Kublai Google account is showing, which means Google recognizes the account.\n\nThe user said \"you're now able to access parsethe.media\" - maybe they fixed the OAuth callback issue. Let me try clicking on the Kublai account and see if the OAuth flow completes successfully this time.\n\nLet me click on the Kublai Kurultai account (ref=e43).The Google OAuth page opened and shows:\n\n1. \"Sign in with Google\"\n2. \"Choose an account to continue to parsethe.media\"\n3. **Kublai Kurultai kublai@kurult.ai** - This is the account the user created for me!\n4. Danny Finn danservfinn@gmail.com\n5. \"Use another account\" option\n\nThe Kublai Google account is showing. The user said \"you're now able to access parsethe.media\" - maybe they fixed the OAuth callback issue. Let me click on the Kublai account and see if the OAuth flow completes successfully this time."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_079a41a49d3f44ebb7520dd9","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","kind":"click","ref":"e43","targetId":"8AA06D80ED0C4408D80B8BED16205D20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1125,"output":604,"cacheRead":154816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":156545,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772747889366}}
