{"type":"message","id":"68f0da52","parentId":"6dca9415","timestamp":"2026-03-05T21:58:45.400Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user clicked on the Kublai Google account and the action was successful (ok: true). The URL has changed to a Google OAuth account chooser/consent URL. This is part of the OAuth flow.\n\nThe URL shows:\n- accounts.google.com/v3/signin/accountchooser\n- client_id=621895521358-8mmeipdg6cjjb9ugkdvjgmces255ud2v.apps.googleusercontent.com\n- redirect_uri=https://www.parsethe.media/api/auth/callback/google\n- response_type=code\n- scope=openid+profile+email\n- service=lso\n- flowName=GeneralOAuthFlow\n\nThis is the Google OAuth flow. The redirect_uri is set to https://www.parsethe.media/api/auth/callback/google which is the Parse callback URL.\n\nEarlier, the OAuth flow would get to the consent screen, but then clicking \"Continue\" would redirect back to the sign-in page without completing the authentication.\n\nThe user said \"you're now able to access parsethe.media\" - maybe they fixed the OAuth callback issue. Let me take a snapshot to see the current state of the page.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"The user clicked on the Kublai Google account and the action was successful (ok: true). The URL has changed to a Google OAuth URL with the redirect_uri set to `https://www.parsethe.media/api/auth/callback/google`.\n\nThis is part of the OAuth flow. Earlier, the OAuth flow would get to the consent screen, but then clicking \"Continue\" would redirect back to the sign-in page without completing the authentication.\n\nThe user said \"you're now able to access parsethe.media\" - maybe they fixed the OAuth callback issue. Let me take a snapshot to see the current state of the page.I clicked on the Kublai Google account and the URL has changed to a Google OAuth URL. Let me take a snapshot to see the current state of the page."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_41a4365af0284de691b8f074","name":"br