{"type":"message","id":"efda1b6c","parentId":"cbcc2a13","timestamp":"2026-03-05T22:32:32.161Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I found the parse-skill! It's at `/Users/kublai/.openclaw/skills/parse-skill`, not in the agents/main/skills directory.\n\nLet me check the status of this parse-skill and see if it was updated by the ACP session.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Found it! The parse-skill is at `/Users/kublai/.openclaw/skills/parse-skill`. Let me check its status:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b57c21ccf51f4a97963cb34b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /Users/kublai/.openclaw/skills/parse-skill/ && echo \"---\" && cat /Users/kublai/.openclaw/skills/parse-skill/SKILL.md 2>/dev/null | head -80"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":883,"output":153,"cacheRead":29184,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30220,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772749945014}}
{"type":"message","id":"fdb3b30d","parentId":"efda1b6c","timestamp":"2026-03-05T22:32:32.197Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_b57c21ccf51f4a97963cb34b","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"total 40\ndrwxr-xr-x   5 kublai  staff    160 Mar  5 17:14 .\ndrwxr-xr-x  50 kublai  staff   1600 Mar  5 13:16 ..\n-rwxr-xr-x   1 kublai  staff    869 Mar  5 17:14 model-map.sh\n-rwxr-xr-x   1 kublai  staff   2367 Mar  5 17:14 parse-test.sh\n-rw-r--r--   1 kublai  staff  12002 Mar  5 17:14 SKILL.md\n---\n---\nname: parse-skill\nversion: 2.0.0\ndescription: \"Parse for Agents: Test and evaluate LLM prompts using OpenRouter\"\nmetadata:\n  openclaw:\n    category: \"productivity\"\n    requires:\n      env: [\"PARSE_API_KEY\", \"OPENROUTER_API_KEY\"]\n---\n\n# Parse for Agents - Agent Skill\n\n## Overview\n\nParse for Agents is a prompt testing and evaluation API. Use this skill to:\n- Test your prompts with real LLM calls via OpenRouter\n- Evaluate output quality (LLM-as-judge scoring)\n- Measure cost and latency\n- Detect prompt injection attempts\n\n**Key: All test calls use the same model the customer is running.** The skill auto-detects the agent's model from `~/.openclaw/config/agents.json` and routes test calls through OpenRouter.\n\n## Authentication\n\n### Parse API Key\nGet one from https://www.parsethe.media/auth/keys\n\n```bash\nexport PARSE_API_KEY=\"parse_pk_...\"\n```\n\n### OpenRouter API Key\nRequired for running LLM test calls. Stored in `~/.openclaw/config/.env`:\n\n```bash\nexport OPENROUTER_API_KEY=\"your-key-here\"\n```\n\n## Model Detection\n\nThe skill automatically detects the customer's model from the OpenClaw agent config:\n\n```bash\n# Auto-detect: reads the calling agent's model from agents.json\nAGENT_MODEL=$(jq -r \".agents[] | select(.id == \\\"$OPENCLAW_AGENT_ID\\\") | .model\" ~/.openclaw/config/agents.json)\n```\n\nIf `OPENCLAW_AGENT_ID` is not set, you can pass the model explicitly. The model is mapped to an OpenRouter-compatible ID automatically.\n\n### Model Mapping\n\n| Agent Config Model | OpenRouter Model ID |\n|---|---|\n| kimi-coding/k2p5 | moonshotai/kimi-k2.5 |\n| deepseek/deepseek-chat | deepseek/deepseek-chat |\n| deepseek/deepseek-reasoner | deepseek/deepseek-reasoner |\n| openai/gpt-4o-mini | openai/gpt-4o-mini |\n| openai/gpt-4o | openai/gpt-4o |\n| anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6 | anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6 |\n| anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5 | anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5 |\n| google/gemini-2.0-flash | google/gemini-2.0-flash-001 |\n| minimax/abab6.5s-chat | minimax/abab6.5s-chat |\n\n## API Endpoints\n\n### POST /api/v1/evaluate\n\nSubmit a prompt evaluation job. The model is auto-detected from the customer's agent config.\n\n**URL:** `https://www.parsethe.media/api/v1/evaluate`\n\n**Headers:**\n```\nContent-Type: application/json\nAuthorization: Bearer parse_pk_...\n```\n\n**Request Body:**\n```json"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":14,"aggregated":"total 40\ndrwxr-xr-x   5 kublai  staff    160 Mar  5 17:14 .\ndrwxr-xr-x  50 kublai  staff   1600 Mar  5 13:16 ..\n-rwxr-xr-x   1 kublai  staff    869 Mar  5 17:14 model-map.sh\n-rwxr-xr-x   1 kublai  staff   2367 Mar  5 17:14 parse-test.sh\n-rw-r--r--   1 kublai  staff  12002 Mar  5 17:14 SKILL.md\n---\n---\nname: parse-skill\nversion: 2.0.0\ndescription: \"Parse for Agents: Test and evaluate LLM prompts using OpenRouter\"\nmetadata:\n  openclaw:\n    category: \"productivity\"\n    requires:\n      env: [\"PARSE_API_KEY\", \"OPENROUTER_API_KEY\"]\n---\n\n# Parse for Agents - Agent Skill\n\n## Overview\n\nParse for Agents is a prompt testing and evaluation API. Use this skill to:\n- Test your prompts with real LLM calls via OpenRouter\n- Evaluate output quality (LLM-as-judge scoring)\n- Measure cost and latency\n- Detect prompt injection attempts\n\n**Key: All test calls use the same model the customer is running.** The skill auto-detects the agent's model from `~/.openclaw/config/agents.json` and routes test calls through OpenRouter.\n\n## Authentication\n\n### Parse API Key\nGet one from https://www.parsethe.media/auth/keys\n\n```bash\nexport PARSE_API_KEY=\"parse_pk_...\"\n```\n\n### OpenRouter API Key\nRequired for running LLM test calls. Stored in `~/.openclaw/config/.env`:\n\n```bash\nexport OPENROUTER_API_KEY=\"your-key-here\"\n```\n\n## Model Detection\n\nThe skill automatically detects the customer's model from the OpenClaw agent config:\n\n```bash\n# Auto-detect: reads the calling agent's model from agents.json\nAGENT_MODEL=$(jq -r \".agents[] | select(.id == \\\"$OPENCLAW_AGENT_ID\\\") | .model\" ~/.openclaw/config/agents.json)\n```\n\nIf `OPENCLAW_AGENT_ID` is not set, you can pass the model explicitly. The model is mapped to an OpenRouter-compatible ID automatically.\n\n### Model Mapping\n\n| Agent Config Model | OpenRouter Model ID |\n|---|---|\n| kimi-coding/k2p5 | moonshotai/kimi-k2.5 |\n| deepseek/deepseek-chat | deepseek/deepseek-chat |\n| deepseek/deepseek-reasoner | deepseek/deepseek-reasoner |\n| openai/gpt-4o-mini | openai/gpt-4o-mini |\n| openai/gpt-4o | openai/gpt-4o |\n| anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6 | anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6 |\n| anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5 | anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5 |\n| google/gemini-2.0-flash | google/gemini-2.0-flash-001 |\n| minimax/abab6.5s-chat | minimax/abab6.5s-chat |\n\n## API Endpoints\n\n### POST /api/v1/evaluate\n\nSubmit a prompt evaluation job. The model is auto-detected from the customer's agent config.\n\n**URL:** `https://www.parsethe.media/api/v1/evaluate`\n\n**Headers:**\n```\nContent-Type: application/json\nAuthorization: Bearer parse_pk_...\n```\n\n**Request Body:**\n```json","cwd":"/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772749952196}}
