{"type":"message","id":"db2290fa","parentId":"389c1661","timestamp":"2026-03-06T00:16:48.325Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, jochi's CLAUDE.md is updated with the spreadsheet skill. Now I need to:\n\n1. Check if main (kublai) has a CLAUDE.md - earlier I saw it doesn't have one\n2. Create one for main with all 4 skills\n3. Optionally update mongke and chagatai to reference the shared skills\n\nLet me check main's directory and create a CLAUDE.md if needed, then also check mongke and chagatai.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Good, jochi is updated. Now let me check if main (kublai) has a CLAUDE.md and create one if not:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e7b7fc2d4d2b40f5a1e1f34a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/agents/main/CLAUDE.md 2>/dev/null || echo \"CLAUDE.md not found for main\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1139,"output":175,"cacheRead":77696,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79010,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772756199836}}
