{"type":"message","id":"0fc2cfa6","parentId":"ddb2b187","timestamp":"2026-03-06T00:31:24.211Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9e2bb3e6d0cf4659b76874be","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"total 96\ndrwxr-xr-x  5 kublai  staff    160 Mar  5 17:58 .\ndrwxr-xr-x  3 kublai  staff     96 Mar  5 00:57 ..\ndrwxr-xr-x  6 kublai  staff    192 Mar  5 01:13 code\n-rw-r--r--  1 kublai  staff  16774 Mar  5 00:59 VISION.md\n-rw-r--r--  1 kublai  staff  27118 Mar  5 17:58 x402-payment-design.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":23,"aggregated":"total 96\ndrwxr-xr-x  5 kublai  staff    160 Mar  5 17:58 .\ndrwxr-xr-x  3 kublai  staff     96 Mar  5 00:57 ..\ndrwxr-xr-x  6 kublai  staff    192 Mar  5 01:13 code\n-rw-r--r--  1 kublai  staff  16774 Mar  5 00:59 VISION.md\n-rw-r--r--  1 kublai  staff  27118 Mar  5 17:58 x402-payment-design.md","cwd":"/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772757084203}}
{"type":"message","id":"8add73d2","parentId":"0fc2cfa6","timestamp":"2026-03-06T00:31:24.242Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_456ba1da73c9467c80928cc4","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# x402 Payment System Design — Parse for Agents\n\n**Date:** 2026-03-05 (Updated)\n**Status:** DESIGN COMPLETE — Ready for Implementation\n**Prior Art:** Horde-Brainstorming diverge/evaluate/converge analysis (2026-03-05)\n**Author:** Kublai\n\n---\n\n## 1. Executive Summary\n\nParse for Agents needs autonomous agent payments. The **x402 protocol** (HTTP 402 Payment Required) is the open standard for agent-to-agent payments, co-founded by Coinbase and Cloudflare, processing 100M+ payments with 156K weekly transactions.\n\nThis document designs a **tiered per-call payment system** using the official `@x402/hono` SDK with USDC stablecoin settlement on Base L2.\n\n**Why x402 over Stripe for agent API:**\n- Agent-native: No accounts, no signup — pay per request autonomously\n- Direct SDK match: `@x402/hono` exists for our exact framework\n- Micropayments: $0.005 per chat message with sub-cent network fees\n- Protocol standard: Backed by Coinbase, Cloudflare, Stripe; integrated with Google AP2\n\nThe main Parse platform (parsethe.media) keeps Stripe for human subscriptions. Parse for Agents uses x402 for machine-to-machine payments. Both coexist.\n\n---\n\n## 2. x402 Protocol Overview\n\n### What Is x402?\n\nx402 activates the long-reserved HTTP 402 \"Payment Required\" status code for instant stablecoin micropayments over HTTP. Launched May 2025 by Coinbase, governed by the neutral x402 Foundation (co-founded with Cloudflare, September 2025).\n\n### Three Roles\n\n```\n┌──────────┐     ┌─────────────────┐     ┌──────────────┐\n│  CLIENT   │────>│  RESOURCE SERVER │────>│  FACILITATOR  │\n│  (Agent)  │<────│  (Parse API)     │<────│  (x402.org)   │\n└──────────┘     └─────────────────┘     └──────────────┘\n```\n\n1. **Client** (AI Agent): Pays per request with signed USDC transfer\n2. **Resource Server** (Parse for Agents): Returns 402 with price, verifies payment\n3. **Facilitator** (x402.org / Coinbase CDP): Verifies signatures, settles on-chain\n\n### Supported Networks\n\n| Network | Chain ID | Tokens | Use Case |\n|---------|----------|--------|----------|\n| Base (Coinbase L2) | eip155:8453 | USDC | **Production (recommended)** |\n| Base Sepolia | eip155:84532 | USDC | Development/testing |"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":14,"aggregated":"# x402 Payment System Design — Parse for Agents\n\n**Date:** 2026-03-05 (Updated)\n**Status:** DESIGN COMPLETE — Ready for Implementation\n**Prior Art:** Horde-Brainstorming diverge/evaluate/converge analysis (2026-03-05)\n**Author:** Kublai\n\n---\n\n## 1. Executive Summary\n\nParse for Agents needs autonomous agent payments. The **x402 protocol** (HTTP 402 Payment Required) is the open standard for agent-to-agent payments, co-founded by Coinbase and Cloudflare, processing 100M+ payments with 156K weekly transactions.\n\nThis document designs a **tiered per-call payment system** using the official `@x402/hono` SDK with USDC stablecoin settlement on Base L2.\n\n**Why x402 over Stripe for agent API:**\n- Agent-native: No accounts, no signup — pay per request autonomously\n- Direct SDK match: `@x402/hono` exists for our exact framework\n- Micropayments: $0.005 per chat message with sub-cent network fees\n- Protocol standard: Backed by Coinbase, Cloudflare, Stripe; integrated with Google AP2\n\nThe main Parse platform (parsethe.media) keeps Stripe for human subscriptions. Parse for Agents uses x402 for machine-to-machine payments. Both coexist.\n\n---\n\n## 2. x402 Protocol Overview\n\n### What Is x402?\n\nx402 activates the long-reserved HTTP 402 \"Payment Required\" status code for instant stablecoin micropayments over HTTP. Launched May 2025 by Coinbase, governed by the neutral x402 Foundation (co-founded with Cloudflare, September 2025).\n\n### Three Roles\n\n```\n┌──────────┐     ┌─────────────────┐     ┌──────────────┐\n│  CLIENT   │────>│  RESOURCE SERVER │────>│  FACILITATOR  │\n│  (Agent)  │<────│  (Parse API)     │<────│  (x402.org)   │\n└──────────┘     └─────────────────┘     └──────────────┘\n```\n\n1. **Client** (AI Agent): Pays per request with signed USDC transfer\n2. **Resource Server** (Parse for Agents): Returns 402 with price, verifies payment\n3. **Facilitator** (x402.org / Coinbase CDP): Verifies signatures, settles on-chain\n\n### Supported Networks\n\n| Network | Chain ID | Tokens | Use Case |\n|---------|----------|--------|----------|\n| Base (Coinbase L2) | eip155:8453 | USDC | **Production (recommended)** |\n| Base Sepolia | eip155:84532 | USDC | Development/testing |","cwd":"/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772757084234}}
{"type":"message","id":"666d8d2e","parentId":"8add73d2","timestamp":"2026-03-06T00:31:24.401Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_15e1d5efb2204c2ebb3bc374","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/Users/kublai/projects/parse-github/src/app/api/v1/route.ts:      paymentRequired: 402,\n/Users/kublai/projects/parse-github/src/app/api/article/analyze-stream/route.ts:          code: 'INSUFFICIENT_CREDITS', // Consistent error code for payment-required\n/Users/kublai/projects/parse-github/src/app/api/article/analyze/route.ts:          code: \"INSUFFICIENT_CREDITS\", // Consistent error code for payment-required\n/Users/kublai/projects/parse-github/src/app/api/credits/purchase/route.ts:    // In production, verify Stripe payment here\n/Users/kublai/projects/parse-github/src/app/api/stripe/webhook/route.ts:        // Handle credit pack purchases (one-time payments)\n/Users/kublai/projects/parse-github/src/app/api/stripe/webhook/route.ts:        if (session.metadata?.type === 'credit_pack' && session.payment_status === 'paid') {\n/Users/kublai/projects/parse-github/src/app/api/stripe/webhook/route.ts:        if (session.metadata?.type === 'subscription' && session.payment_status === 'paid') {\n/Users/kublai/projects/parse-github/src/app/api/stripe/webhook/route.ts:      case 'invoice.payment_failed': {\n/Users/kublai/projects/parse-github/src/app/api/stripe/webhook/route.ts:    await markEventProcessed(eventId, 'invoice.payment_failed', 'unknown', { error: 'No subscription ID', invoiceId: invoice.id })\n/Users/kublai/projects/parse-github/src/app/api/stripe/webhook/route.ts:    await markEventProcessed(eventId, 'invoice.payment_failed', 'unknown', { error: 'Subscription not found', subscriptionId })"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":142,"aggregated":"/Users/kublai/projects/parse-github/src/app/api/v1/route.ts:      paymentRequired: 402,\n/Users/kublai/projects/parse-github/src/app/api/article/analyze-stream/route.ts:          code: 'INSUFFICIENT_CREDITS', // Consistent error code for payment-required\n/Users/kublai/projects/parse-github/src/app/api/article/analyze/route.ts:          code: \"INSUFFICIENT_CREDITS\", // Consistent error code for payment-required\n/Users/kublai/projects/parse-github/src/app/api/credits/purchase/route.ts:    // In production, verify Stripe payment here\n/Users/kublai/projects/parse-github/src/app/api/stripe/webhook/route.ts:        // Handle credit pack purchases (one-time payments)\n/Users/kublai/projects/parse-github/src/app/api/stripe/webhook/route.ts:        if (session.metadata?.type === 'credit_pack' && session.payment_status === 'paid') {\n/Users/kublai/projects/parse-github/src/app/api/stripe/webhook/route.ts:        if (session.metadata?.type === 'subscription' && session.payment_status === 'paid') {\n/Users/kublai/projects/parse-github/src/app/api/stripe/webhook/route.ts:      case 'invoice.payment_failed': {\n/Users/kublai/projects/parse-github/src/app/api/stripe/webhook/route.ts:    await markEventProcessed(eventId, 'invoice.payment_failed', 'unknown', { error: 'No subscription ID', invoiceId: invoice.id })\n/Users/kublai/projects/parse-github/src/app/api/stripe/webhook/route.ts:    await markEventProcessed(eventId, 'invoice.payment_failed', 'unknown', { error: 'Subscription not found', subscriptionId })","cwd":"/Users/kublai/.openclaw/agents/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772757084393}}
{"type":"message","id":"fe953656","parentId":"666d8d2e","timestamp":"2026-03-06T00:31:43.011Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I have the status:\n\n1. **Design Document**: The x402-payment-design.md file exists and is comprehensive (27KB). Status: DESIGN COMPLETE — Ready for Implementation\n\n2. **Parse Codebase**: There are references to payment/credits/Stripe but no x402 implementation yet. The current payment system uses:\n- Stripe for subscriptions and credit packs\n- A credit-based system (INSUFFICIENT_CREDITS error)\n- No x402-specific code found\n\n3. **Implementation Status**: NOT STARTED. The design is complete, but the actual x402 integration has not been implemented yet.\n\nLet me provide a clear status summary to the user.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Here's the status of the x402 pay-as-you-go implementation for Parse for Agents:\n\n---\n\n## x402 Implementation Status\n\n**Design:** COMPLETE\n**Implementation:** NOT STARTED\n\n---\n\n### What's Done\n\n**Design Document** (`x402-payment-design.md` - 27KB):\n- x402 protocol overview (HTTP 402 for agent payments)\n- Pricing model: Tiered per-call ($0.005 - $0.15 per request)\n- SDK: `@x402/hono` for Hono framework\n- Network: USDC on Base L2\n- Architecture: Client → Resource Server → Facilitator flow\n- API endpoint design with payment verification\n\n### What's NOT Done\n\n**Code Implementation:**\n- No `@x402/hono` middleware installed\n- No payment verification in API routes\n- No wallet/address configuration\n- No x402-specific endpoints\n\n### Current Parse Payment System\n\nThe existing Parse codebase uses:\n- Stripe for subscriptions and credit packs\n- Credit-based system (not per-call)\n- No agent-native payment support\n\n---\n\n### Next Steps to Implement\n\n1. Install `@x402/hono` SDK\n2. Add payment middleware to API routes\n3. Configure Base L2 wallet for receiving payments\n4. Update API endpoints to return 402 with pricing\n5. Test with agent clients\n\n---\n\nWant me to spawn a session to implement the x402 payment system?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1525,"output":444,"cacheRead":107136,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109105,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772757084401}}
