jects/parse-for-agents/x402-payment-design.md\n\n## Key Requirements\n1. Install `@x402/hono` SDK\n2. Add payment middleware to API routes\n3. Configure Base L2 wallet for receiving USDC payments\n4. Update API endpoints to return 402 with pricing\n5. Implement payment verification before processing requests\n\n## Pricing (from design)\n| Endpoint | Depth/Mode | Price |\n|----------|-----------|-------|\n| POST /v1/analyze | quick | $0.01 |\n| POST /v1/analyze | standard | $0.05 |\n| POST /v1/analyze | deep | $0.15 |\n| POST /v1/evaluate | default | $0.01 |\n| POST /v1/chat | per message | $0.005 |\n| GET endpoints | - | FREE |\n\n## Parse Project Location\n/Users/kublai/projects/parse-github/\n\n## Success Criteria\n- @x402/hono middleware installed and configured\n- API endpoints return 402 with pricing when payment required\n- Payment verification works before processing paid requests\n- Free endpoints (GET /v1/models, GET /v1/pricing) remain free\n- Test with a sample request to verify 402 response\n\n## Notes\n- The main Parse platform keeps Stripe for human subscriptions\n- This x402 integration is for agent-to-agent payments only\n- Use /horde-plan first to plan the implementation, then /horde-implement"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"zai-coding","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":113697,"output":739,"cacheRead":8768,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123204,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772758091720}}
